@startuml

title Information flow — downward (constraint)

skinparam rectangle {
    BackgroundColor #2A2A2E
    BorderColor #58A6FF
    FontColor #E3E3E6
}
skinparam note {
    BackgroundColor #1A1A1E
    BorderColor #58A6FF
    FontColor #E3E3E6
}
skinparam ArrowColor #8AB4F8
skinparam ArrowFontColor #E3E3E6
skinparam BackgroundColor transparent
skinparam DefaultFontColor #E3E3E6

rectangle "Product identity\n(S5)"    as Identity
rectangle "Version identity\n(S4)"    as Version
rectangle "Sprint mission\n(S3)"      as Sprint
rectangle "Story goal\n(S2)"          as Story
rectangle "Task goal\n(S1)"           as Task

Identity --> Version : constrains
Version  --> Sprint  : constrains
Sprint   --> Story   : constrains
Story    --> Task    : constrains

note right of Identity
  Each higher level
  constrains the space
  of acceptable
  lower-level work.
end note

@enduml
